#

Black Bean and Corn Tacos

20 min
$10
600 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

dairy

Dietary Tags:

vegetariangluten-free

Cuisine:

Mexican

Course:

Main

Tags:

easyquicktacos

Description

Deliciously spiced black bean and corn tacos topped with fresh avocado and a squeeze of lime.

Ingredients

  • corn tortillas: 4
  • canned black beans: 1 can (15 oz)
  • fresh corn: 1 cup
  • ripe avocado: 1
  • fresh cilantro: 1/4 cup
  • lime: 1
  • sour cream: 1/4 cup
  • shredded cheese: 1/2 cup
